*all_updates** for Fedora packager into\r\n  system settings (/et/dnfdragora/dnfdragora.yaml)  to change this behaviour and show All the packages with To_update filter (see dnfdragora.yaml.example)\r\n- try to avoid crash on exit from dnfdragora-update (https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1839784\r\n  and https://bugzilla.redhat.com/show_bug.cgi?id=1844707)\r\n"}
